<section>
    <div class="inner-section" id="the-issue">
        <h2 class="title"
            data-sal-repeat="data-sal-repeat"
            data-sal="slide-right"
            data-sal-duration="1000"
            data-sal-easing="ease-out-back">The
            Issue.</h2>
        <p data-sal-repeat="data-sal-repeat"
            data-sal="slide-right"
            data-sal-duration="1000"
            data-sal-easing="ease-out-back">
            Compared with other universities
            around the country, our voting rate is
            down. This, on top of the fact college
            students generally
            vote at a much lower rate than the
            average citizen.
            According to
            <a class="link"
                href="assets/General-Election-NSLVE-Data.pdf"
                target="_blank">our campus
                report</a>
            from the National Study of Learning,
            Voting, and Education, fewer than half
            of UVM undergrads voted in the
            last general election.
        </p>

        <p data-sal-repeat="data-sal-repeat"
            data-sal="slide-right"
            data-sal-duration="1000"
            data-sal-easing="ease-out-back"
            class="bold">We can fix this.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="inner-section"
        id="greater-vision">

        <img class="lazy"
            src="/assets/images/lizAndAidanPlaceholder.svg"
            data-src="/assets/images/lizAndAidan.webp"
            alt="Picture of UVM Votes members carving pumpkins."
            data-sal-repeat="data-sal-repeat"
            data-sal="zoom-in"
            data-sal-duration="1000"
            data-sal-easing="ease-out-back">

        <h2 class="title"
            data-sal-repeat="data-sal-repeat"
            data-sal="slide-right"
            data-sal-duration="1000"
            data-sal-easing="ease-out-back">The
            Solution</h2>
        <p data-sal-repeat="data-sal-repeat"
            data-sal="slide-right"
            data-sal-duration="1000"
            data-sal-easing="ease-out-back">
            Institutionalize voting; take
            advantage of UVM's ability to access
            thousands of students in a unique way
            which other clubs or groups simply
            can't. Here are some of the projects
            we're currently working on:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Give students election day off as
                a campus-wide holiday, consistent
                with <a class="link"
                    target="_blank"
                    href="https://www.to2v.org/student-body-president-letter">the
                    letter the SGA signed</a>.
            </li>
            <li>Have UVM text every student a link
                to <a class="link" target="_blank"
                    href="https://uvm.turbovote.org">Turbo
                    Vote</a>.</li>
            <li>Integrate voter registration into
                student orientation days.</li>
            <li>Add a polling site for the <a
                    class="link" target="_blank"
                    href="https://vtcynic.com/news/a-gerrymandered-student-ward-how-burlingtons-ward-8-got-its-shape/">gerrymandered
                    student ward</a>.</li>
            <li>Bring voter registration to clubs,
                fraternities, and sororities.</li>
            <li>Research how to make SGA elections
                more competitive.</li>
        </ul>

        <div id="sign-up">
            <form name="Role request"
                method="POST" data-netlify="true"
                data-sal-repeat="data-sal-repeat"
                data-sal="zoom-in"
                data-sal-duration="1000"
                data-sal-easing="ease-out-back">
                <h3>Get Involved!</h3>
                <div class="user-box">
                    <input type="text" name="name"
                        required="" />
                    <label>Email:</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-bottom">
                    <div class="quick-fix-thanks">
                        <label>
                            <input type="radio"
                                name="interest"
                                value="Volunteer"
                                checked="checked">
                            Volunteer
                        </label>
                        <label>
                            <input type="radio"
                                name="interest"
                                value="Organize">
                            Organize
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    <button
                        class="link-btn bg-blue"
                        type="submit">Submit</button>
                </div>

            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

